Do. Or do not. There is no try... I am afraid my friend that today you need to choose your side. You can choose the light path of the righteous or sinister dark. The choice is yours if you have updated to the latest iOS 13.

BIGGEST update ever! We are adding a whole new feature Goals. From now you can set your own goals and track them just by using Daylio as usually. Make sure you reach your goals and get sweet achievements! Thank you for using Daylio your ratings and your comments.
We have a special treat for all Daylio supporters. Now you can create your own color themes. Go ahead make Daylio yours and share your theme with the world! daylio
